## 7. Technical Specifications

### 7.1 Recommended Tech Stack
**Frontend**: Flutter (iOS & Android support)
**Local Database**: SQLite with Hive for caching
**Backend**: Supabase (Recommended for SQL needs)
  - PostgreSQL Database
  - Supabase Auth (individual credentials)
  - Realtime subscriptions
  - Storage for documents
**State Management**: Riverpod
**Offline Sync**: Custom sync engine with conflict resolution
**Push Notifications**: Firebase Cloud Messaging (for fee reminders)

### 7.2 Development Timeline
**Phase 1: Foundation** (4 weeks)
- Authentication system (individual logins)
- Basic seat management (160 seats)
- Student CRUD with edit permissions
- Local database setup

**Phase 2: Core Features** (5 weeks)
- Fee management with edit capability
- Seat assignment system
- Add more seats feature
- Basic reporting

**Phase 3: Advanced Features** (4 weeks)
- Advanced reporting engine
- Offline sync implementation
- Audit logging system
- User management

**Phase 4: Polish & Testing** (3 weeks)
- UI/UX refinements
- Performance optimization
- Security testing
- User training materials

**Total**: 16 weeks (4 months)

