## 11. Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|------------|--------|------------|
| Data sync conflicts | Medium | High | Implement conflict resolution strategy |
| Internet connectivity issues | High | Medium | Robust offline mode with clear indicators |
| User error in fee editing | Medium | Medium | Audit trails and confirmation dialogs |
| Seat expansion complexity | Low | Low | Simple add seats interface with validation |
| Performance with 160+ seats | Low | Medium | Virtual scrolling and pagination |
| Security breaches | Low | High | Encryption, secure auth, regular audits |

## 12. Assumptions

1. Initial library capacity: 160 seats (expandable)
2. Three users initially, expandable later
3. All admins have equal editing permissions for students and fees
4. Internet available periodically for sync (not 24/7)
5. Library operates 6 days a week
6. Student records retained for minimum 2 years
7. Monthly fee cycle follows calendar month

## 13. Constraints

1. Budget: Fixed development budget
2. Timeline: 4-month delivery timeline
3. Platform: Must support Android 9+ and iOS 13+
4. Data Privacy: Compliance with local data protection laws
5. Offline Requirement: Must function 8+ hours without internet

